Openmeetings provides video conferencing, instant messaging, white
board, collaborative document editing and other groupware tools
using API functions of the Red5 Streaming Server for Remoting and
Streaming.

Openmeetings requires a user/group, by default 'openmeetings' is used.
A different user/group can be used via:

  # OMUSER=nobody OMGROUP=nobody ./apache-openmeetings.SlackBuild
